{"tid":712340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來真係有【謝賢：咩話40比0】電競上海龍之隊打四十場輸足曬","createTime":"2018-06-22T04:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T00:28:55.000Z","uid":173631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4639ef03babc05b9c273b1336f901887197db211","tid":712340,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-421867850e8a01a5089bbd1937fe69d3_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-421867850e8a01a5089bbd1937fe69d3_hd.jpg&h=23f4ec34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.dadianjing.cn/ec/201806/17/1529206898_3587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.dadianjing.cn%2Fec%2F201806%2F17%2F1529206898_3587.jpg&h=f92b46fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國上海龍 OWL 157 天一勝未取，40 連敗持續破上限<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%BE%8D-owl-%E9%A6%96%E5%AD%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%8B%9D%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%8C40-%E9%80%A3%E6%95%97%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%A0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90-040144448.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.esports.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25BE%258D-owl-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%258B%259D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%258F%2596%25EF%25BC%258C40-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E6%2595%2597%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2599%2590-040144448.html&d=%2BRw2xM0Hd4f155oiEcL3Q8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4a72ba85\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.esports.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%BE%8D-owl-%E9%A6%96%E5%AD%A3%E4%B8%80%E5%8B%9D%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%96%EF%BC%8C40-%E9%80%A3%E6%95%97%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E7%A0%B4%E4%B8%8A%E9%99%90-040144448.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《鬥陣特攻》職業電競聯賽（Overwatch League，簡稱 OWL）階段四今（17）日正式結束，僅剩下明日的階段決賽，也代表首季的例行賽賽程全部 Over，而中國上海龍之隊在 0-4 敗給<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舊金山震動隊後，成了季賽間唯一一勝未取的隊伍，40 連敗也持續突破世界紀錄。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n上海龍之隊在 7 日時曾與同樣墊底的聯盟隊伍佛羅里達狂歡隊戰滿五盤，那是他們在首季最接近勝利的時刻。雖然在第三階段時，引進了來自南韓的 Geguri 與來自中國聯賽冠軍 Miraculous Youngster 的 Sky 等選手，但講求團隊作戰的鬥陣僅靠兩三人是無法輕易就拿下勝利的 &mdash; 尤其是對方的實力比你更強時。<br />\n<br />\n上海龍並未在社群媒體上表示太多，僅祝賀舊金山的好表現，並誓言下季會捲土重來。而從 8 月起到 12 月 1 日前，OWL 將進入漫長的簽約期，上海龍的問題不僅是更換選手那麼簡單，從上至下的大整頓或許是必要的，我們就一起期待在明年時上海是否能夠真的成為一條「龍」吧。"},{"pid":"f4c0e16e5d4bb15274fe9b10ce14816223bea8f5","tid":712340,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"改名做0WIN算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f34dbb874b4b86d805838d4a7e6295ae235c06","tid":712340,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T00:28:55.000Z","msg":"支那仔學人玩團隊合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}